会化和<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w24587">广泛共享繁荣</a>的进步目标最终与赢得二战和建立美国高科技制造业的实业家目标一致。</p><p>当然，那是很久以前的事了，技术已经发生了变化。但没有理由相信工会与现代高科技制造业不相容。 <a href="https://conversableeconomist.blogspot.com/2016/09/union-density-and-collective-bargaining.html">考虑一下这样一个事实</a>：德国和日本等国家的工会化率比美国高得多，而且德国的集体谈判覆盖率也高<em>得多</em>，这是由于所谓的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sectoral_collective_bargaining">部门谈判</a>，甚至让非工会工人也受到工会协议的覆盖： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3951b72-8cf9-4cc8-b387-6fb788a4d4fa_677x781.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3951b72-8cf9-4cc8-b387-6fb788a4d4fa_677x781.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3951b72-8cf9-4cc8-b387-6fb788a4d4fa_677x781.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3951b72-8cf9-4cc8-b387-6fb788a4d4fa_677x781.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3951b72-8cf9-4cc8-b387-6fb788a4d4fa_677x781.jpeg" width="677" height="781" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a3951b72-8cf9-4cc8-b387-6fb788a4d4fa_677x781.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:781,&quot;width&quot;:677,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1